                     <interp inst="t18731124-35-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, Stealing 13 1/2 lbs., 10 lbs., and 10 lbs. of leather, of <persName id="t18731124-name-176" type="victimName">
